channel.title: Comments on: Where in the WoW?

item.title: By: Foton
item.dc:creator: Foton
item.description: Yep, the entrance to Booty Bay. I usually don't look up either going into the BB, but the one day I was waiting for pirate repop, looked up and whatdoyaknow, the goblins have hauled a pirate ship mast up there. They're so industrious.
item.content:encoded: Yep, the entrance to Booty Bay. I usually don’t look up either going into the BB, but the one day I was waiting for pirate repop, looked up and whatdoyaknow, the goblins have hauled a pirate ship mast up there. They’re so industrious.
